{"tid":1466743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想成功我教唔到，唔想失敗入黎睇完先屌我","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T18:24:21.000Z","uid":266424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e97177b694dfa5fc8fa07e4e5686e444e66f6c17","tid":1466743,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"係！我係p牌，但今日同朋友理論。得到一個結果<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比政府<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">標籤化</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 唔可以帶其他國家國旗出黎<br />\n被屈攪港獨，馬上轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">暴力</span></strong>對待唔關事既人<br />\n被屈暴力就會立刻剷除<br />\n<br />\n3. 說出<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">尊重一國兩制</span></strong>，強烈要求準確確切實行一國兩制的優勢<br />\n要求國家証明國家是以法治國治泡，捉拿破壞份子，剷除企圖破壞或危害一國兩制的警察，証明依法治港<br />\n<br />\n4. 說出我們不是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>港獨</strong></span><br />\n我們現在要求的是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong></span>，與港獨無關<br />\n<br />\n我係冷氣軍師，但我有發夢，可以問我攞相。<br />\n如果大家覺得我係鬼或者分化撚就屌9我，但我唔想失敗係on9既地方，認為我有其中一個point係岩既都去考慮下。<br />\n<br />\n利申 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">核彈都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2d08278c6055e831ea18736b0ccdc17edcd4129","tid":1466743,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3b5e6af050e07e09bac713261d21d401f51a7ed2","tid":1466743,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"a77f8051750822e5ba49e5c6a096773bb995ee1e","tid":1466743,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:12:49.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"b302b8397b4aba7dd6e9d48508915af934e46e73","tid":1466743,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"再推一次就算了，p牌冇人理"}]}